means even though the words aren&#39;t there, means that we&#39;re wonderful interpersonally

36
00:03:07,030 --> 00:03:11,030
and it&#39;s also the price you pay then to go along to a psychic and trip yourself up, thinking

37
00:03:11,030 --> 00:03:13,319
that they can actually predict the future.

38
00:03:13,319 --> 00:03:19,629
All these different mechanisms are at play. To me, what&#39;s interesting is it doesn&#39;t look

39
00:03:19,629 --> 00:03:23,440
like that. It looks like you go in; this person tells you all about yourself; predicts something

40
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:28,190
about the future; comes true; isn&#39;t that incredible? Actually, it&#39;s quite complicated. There isn&#39;t

41
00:03:28,190 --> 00:03:31,709
one psychology there. There are several psychological mechanisms.

42
00:03:31,709 --> 00:03:37,370
It seems a common explanation for these kind of beliefs, especially if you&#39;re a non-believer in the

43
00:03:37,370 --> 00:03:42,739
paranormal is, &quot;People are just stupid; they&#39;ll believe anything&quot;. But you mentioned that there

44
