be a small one, but it&#39;s not particularly striking.

50
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:20,699
I think what&#39;s happening is that a lot of people want to believe in this stuff. Why

51
00:04:20,699 --> 00:04:26,820
else would you go to psychic? You are probably looking for some sort of guidance. So I always

52
00:04:26,820 --> 00:04:31,389
