53
00:04:31,389 --> 00:04:34,919
&quot;What are the symptoms?&quot; You say, &quot;Well, you&#39;re the expert. You tell me.&quot; It would be a ridiculous

54
00:04:34,919 --> 00:04:39,300
thing to say—the two of you are there to work on the problem together. I think that&#39;s

55
